    <title>Python爬虫实战——外网爬取加页面滚动</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/Python%E7%88%AC%E8%99%AB%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%A4%96%E7%BD%91%E7%88%AC%E5%8F%96%E5%8A%A0%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E6%BB%9A%E5%8A%A8%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/Python%E7%88%AC%E8%99%AB%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%A4%96%E7%BD%91%E7%88%AC%E5%8F%96%E5%8A%A0%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E6%BB%9A%E5%8A%A8%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA/</id>
    <published>2023-06-09T04:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-06-11T04:09:09.459Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="项目背景介绍">项目背景介绍</h1><p>我们想要研究国外的华语报刊和内地普通话报刊在词汇使用上的异同，因此首先我们需要对不同国家的报刊资料进行爬取。我们选定的国家为马来西亚，想要爬取的报刊网址为<a class="link" href="https://www.sinchew.com.my/">https://www.sinchew.com.my/<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a> 和<a class="link" href="https://www.chinapress.com.my/">https://www.chinapress.com.my/<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a>，我们会在这两个网站上分别摘取一些文章，使得文章总篇数为100篇左右。同时对于内地的报刊，我们选用的是<a class="link" href="http://www.people.com.cn/">http://www.people.com.cn/<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a> 和 <a class="link" href="http://paper.news.cn/">http://paper.news.cn/<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a>，同样爬取100篇左右的内容即可。几个网站的网页分别展示如下：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/sinchew_first_page.2g6lejzvscw0.webp"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/chinapress_first_page.3enc7yua01u0.webp"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/people_first_page.6p56zf8conw0.webp"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/xinhua_first_page.5xe9ykmm29o0.webp"></p><h1 id="sinchew网站爬虫实战">Sinchew网站爬虫实战</h1><h2 id="第一步文章链接爬取">第一步：文章链接爬取</h2><p>该爬虫我将使用requests+bs4完成，需要导入的库为：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> requests</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> bs4 <span class="keyword">import</span> BeautifulSoup</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>首先我们实现一个最基础的获取网页的框架：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">url1 = <span class="string">r&quot;https://www.sinchew.com.my&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># get html using header</span></span><br><span class="line">headers = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;User-Agent&quot;</span>:<span class="string">&quot;Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/114.0.0.0 Safari/537.36&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Accept&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Accept-Language&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;en-us&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Connection&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;keep-alive&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Accept-Charset&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;GB2312,utf-8;q=0.7,*;q=0.7&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">r = requests.get(url1, headers=headers)</span><br><span class="line">soup = BeautifulSoup(r.content, <span class="string">&quot;html.parser&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>我们将会发现以上代码是无法获得对应网站的响应的，无论当前主机上是否开启了代理，这是因为这个网站实际上是需要翻墙才能登录的，因此我们需要先考虑怎么使得爬虫能够识别代理。以我使用的Clash为例，我们可以从Clash的常规页面的第一项端口看到，这里使用的端口是7890：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/Clash.2bj3v1vgz0w0.webp"></p><p>于是我们应该将以上代码修改为：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">url1 = <span class="string">r&quot;https://www.sinchew.com.my/category/%E5%85%A8%E5%9B%BD/%E5%8D%B3%E6%97%B6%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85/&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># get html using header</span></span><br><span class="line">headers = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;User-Agent&quot;</span>:<span class="string">&quot;Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/114.0.0.0 Safari/537.36&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Accept&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Accept-Language&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;en-us&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Connection&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;keep-alive&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Accept-Charset&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;GB2312,utf-8;q=0.7,*;q=0.7&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">proxies=&#123;<span class="string">&#x27;http&#x27;</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;http://127.0.0.1:7890&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;https&#x27;</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;http://127.0.0.1:7890&#x27;</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line">r = requests.get(url1, headers=headers, proxies=proxies)</span><br><span class="line">soup = BeautifulSoup(r.content, <span class="string">&quot;html.parser&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>实际上也就是添加了proxies参数而已，在这里proxies最后两项的7890应该修改为你对应的端口。</p><p>前面我们只算是完成了前期准备工作，要完成第一部分内容的爬取，我们首先需要获得对应的新闻网页链接，我们首先选择:zap:国内:bookmark:即时国内这个栏目，用小箭头点到对应的链接上，我们找到两个有较明显关系的层次（divclass="desc desc-desktop" 和 a class="internalLink"），展示如下：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/sinchew_crawl_select_page.1h5yk1yr2934.webp"></p><p>我们需要将其转为BeautifulSoup支持的select语法，同时将所有的href提取出来，也就是这么写：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">links = soup.select(<span class="string">&#x27;[class=&quot;desc desc-desktop&quot;] a[class=&quot;internalLink&quot;]&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">links = [link.get(<span class="string">&#x27;href&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">for</span> link <span class="keyword">in</span> links]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接下来就会展现一个文章列表，该列表存储的就是我们能得到的页面啦~</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/sinchew_part1_code.5jspovyd8s00.webp"></p><p>但我们会发现，欸怎么只有这么几条，远远达不到我们想要拿到的数量呀，我们回到源网页看看，结果发现原来页面是下滑滚动加载的，我们点击Network下勾选XHR这个小标签，会发现这个部分一直有资源弹出。事实上是当我们向下滚动鼠标滑轮时，左侧栏内的数据包会实现自动加载，这是使用<a class="link" href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/AJAX/8425">Ajax<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a>异步加载技术实现的。</p><figure><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/sinchew_roll_xhr.1tsgkcxr2qh.webp" alt="sinchew_roll_xhr"><figcaption aria-hidden="true">sinchew_roll_xhr</figcaption></figure><p>我们接下来可以点一下这些随着滚轮下滑新出现的数据包观察一下，我们立刻就会发现很有趣的事：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/sinchew_cat_roll.76jx0xkdt000.webp"></p><p>这里很明目张胆地告诉了我们page=3，再往前面翻一下另一个带有<font color="#008000">?cat=471</font>字样的数据包，我们打开之后发现内容几乎没有改变，也仅仅只是page从3变成了2，这就告诉我们该请求的基准URL （由于还未拼接查询参数，所以称之为基准URL）为<font color="Blue">https://www.sinchew.com.my/ajx-api/category_posts/?cat=471</font>，且由后面的一连串东西我们至少能知道他们的查询参数具有如下规律：</p><blockquote><p>page: 控制页面</p><p>posts_per_page:控制每页显示的文章数量（这和我们前面爬取出来只有10篇文章非常符合）</p></blockquote><p>将这里的page设置为4之后直接在浏览器打开显示的结果如下：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/cat_result.egsjdanz880.webp" style="zoom:200%;"></p><p>我们可以从这个列表中获得对应的permalink，这个就是我们最终需要的文章链接了。另外我其实试过能不能修改posts_per_page来使得直接查一次就能获取足够多的网页，但实际上没什么卵用，还是老老实实去爬吧。</p><p>在写新的爬虫命令时我们需要注意的点是，现在我们的数据是json格式，那就简单啦！直接读取json数据的格式并提取对应数据项的permalink属性就完事了！代码如下：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">headers = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;User-Agent&quot;</span>:<span class="string">&quot;Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/114.0.0.0 Safari/537.36&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Accept&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Accept-Language&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;en-us&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Connection&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;keep-alive&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Accept-Charset&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;GB2312,utf-8;q=0.7,*;q=0.7&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">proxies=&#123;<span class="string">&#x27;http&#x27;</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;http://127.0.0.1:7890&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;https&#x27;</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;http://127.0.0.1:7890&#x27;</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line">link_sinchew = []</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">10</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    url = <span class="string">r&quot;https://www.sinchew.com.my/ajx-api/category_posts/?cat=471&amp;page=&quot;</span>+<span class="built_in">str</span>(i+<span class="number">1</span>)+<span class="string">&quot;&amp;nooffset=true&amp;editorialcat=0&amp;posts_per_pages=10&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    r = requests.get(url, headers=headers, proxies=proxies).json()</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> page_li <span class="keyword">in</span> r:</span><br><span class="line">        link_sinchew.append(page_li[<span class="string">&quot;permalink&quot;</span>])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>爬取的结果如下，但我们不能保证这100条新闻没有重复的，毕竟一般来说如果最后超出了范围，后面很可能所有数据都是一样的：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/link_sinchew.4dge4jrgees0.webp" alt="link_sinchew"></p><p>我们可以通过一个简单的代码来实现去重：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">link_sinchew = <span class="built_in">list</span>(<span class="built_in">set</span>(link_sinchew))</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">len</span>(link_sinchew)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>我们最后得到了83条无重复的链接。</p><h2 id="第二步文章内容爬取及整理">第二步：文章内容爬取及整理</h2><p>有了前面的文章链接，我们接下来可以愉快地进行正文部分的爬取啦！我们随意点开一个链接进去看看文章结果是怎样的：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/sinchew_content.2h9zaamtfom0.webp" alt="sinchew_content"></p><p>可以发现这个文章的html结构着实简单的不行，直接把所有divclass="article-page-content"下的p属性节点拿出来就好了。具体实现也就照猫画虎罢了：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/sinchew_get_content.1bf34t7rd7r4.webp" alt="sinchew_get_content"></p><p>整理一下我们可以获得能顺着链接爬取所有文章的代码如下，这波还温馨的加了进度条功能：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> time</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> tqdm <span class="keyword">import</span> tqdm</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> pandas <span class="keyword">as</span> pd</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">text_sinchew = []</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> url_ui <span class="keyword">in</span> tqdm(<span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="built_in">len</span>(link_sinchew))):</span><br><span class="line">    time.sleep(<span class="number">0.5</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    url = link_sinchew[url_ui]</span><br><span class="line">    r = requests.get(url, headers=headers, proxies=proxies)</span><br><span class="line">    soup = BeautifulSoup(r.content, <span class="string">&quot;html.parser&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    content = soup.select(<span class="string">&#x27;[class=&quot;article-page-content&quot;] p&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    i_te = <span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> content:</span><br><span class="line">        i_te += i.text</span><br><span class="line">    text_sinchew.append(i_te)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">df = pd.DataFrame(text_sinchew)</span><br><span class="line">df.to_excel(<span class="string">&quot;data/sinchew.xlsx&quot;</span>, index=<span class="literal">False</span>, header=<span class="literal">False</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>结果如下：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/text_sinchew.5nuu15uegp40.webp" alt="text_sinchew"></p><h1 id="chinapress网站爬虫实战">ChinaPress网站爬虫实战</h1><p>首先我们如法炮制，打开首页观察可以爬取的信息，但我们发现首页的内容类型太过复杂，有视频类型也有图片类型，还有不少需要滑动才能加载的内容，因此我们选择了其中一个类目，我们将爬取该类目下的文章，在这里我们选择的类目是时事：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/chinapress_时事page.z4vv81agsbk.webp" alt="chinapress_时事page"></p><p>我们可以沿用之前的代码如法炮制，我们同样得到下面这样一个list，一共有21条链接：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/chinapress_simple_crawl.3dohe9aso9i0.webp" alt="chinapress_simple_crawl"></p><p>但这次链接数少的原因和上次不太一样，应该说更好解决，因为我们滑到页面底部，我们欣喜地发现这里有一个下一页按钮，OHYEAH！当我们点进第二页，我们会非常自然且顺滑地发现链接的网址是如此地简单：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/chinapress_second_page.7boc98sau5g0.webp" alt="chinapress_second_page"></p><p>那我们也就不用客气了，直接一气呵成写完它：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">link_chinapress = []</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">10</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    url = <span class="string">r&quot;https://www.chinapress.com.my/category/%e6%97%b6%e4%ba%8b/page/&quot;</span> + <span class="built_in">str</span>(i+<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    r = requests.get(url, headers=headers, proxies=proxies)</span><br><span class="line">    soup = BeautifulSoup(r.content, <span class="string">&quot;html.parser&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    links = soup.select(<span class="string">&#x27;[class=&quot;category_page_post_content&quot;] a&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    links = [link.get(<span class="string">&#x27;href&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">for</span> link <span class="keyword">in</span> links]</span><br><span class="line">    link_chinapress.extend(links)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">link_chinapress = <span class="built_in">list</span>(<span class="built_in">set</span>(link_chinapress))</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="built_in">len</span>(link_chinapress))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>最后结果保存下来了237条新闻链接。下一步和之前做的一样，我们看看其中一条链接的文章长什么样：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/chinapress_content.31q3hsic0zs0.webp" alt="chinapress_content"></p><p>好吧，和之前没什么区别，我们直接上代码：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/chinapress_crawl_content.1teoni3qvfy8.webp" alt="chinapress_crawl_content"></p><p>这里我们发现一个小小的问题，每一个爬下来的内容最后都加了一个ADVERTISEMENTADVERTISEMENT，我们在代码里加上下面这句将其删掉就好。实际上我们在完成爬虫之后还是需要做一定数据预处理的，这是后话。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">i_te = i_te.replace(<span class="string">&quot;ADVERTISEMENTADVERTISEMENT&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="人民网爬虫实战">人民网爬虫实战</h1><p>与前面相对应，我们在这里选取的是国际版面。实际上在做数据分析之前我们就可以看出，人民网和新华社的内容均是偏官方的，并没有像Sinchew和ChinaPress一样“地道”。Anyway我们先看看对应的数据格式：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/人民网_link.5mn946a1zh.webp" alt="人民网_link"></p><h2 id="第一个问题爬取内容的合理性">第一个问题：爬取内容的合理性</h2><p>可以发现该部分的链接基本都是以列表形式呈现的，这样其实很好处理，似乎我们只需要选取列表的标签就好了：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/人民网_simple_crawl.3y9x0nqy0wo0.webp" alt="人民网_simple_crawl"></p><p>但我们再仔细一看其实是有问题的，因为这里夹杂了很多我们用不到的内容，我们就直接点进蓝色字的链接，会发现这些链接只有一句描述图片的文字，并没有我们需要的实际内容，且对于其他内容也有较多是人物相关的，我们想要获取需要的列表内容可以做两步筛除，第一步是删除掉带有html等字样的链接，第二步是删除以index.html结尾的链接，这样应该就是我们需要的列表结果了。</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/人民网_simple_crawl_problem.4jqyhnu76y20.webp" alt="人民网_simple_crawl_problem"></p><p>但我们对列表里的内容仍不满意，因为内容的篇幅较小，我们接着查找可以发现有另一个栏目叫做headingNews：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/人民网_headingNews.3dq5nm82le00.webp" alt="人民网_headingNews"></p><p>我们发现最下面又有翻页的按钮，这让我们再次灵机一动，果不其然，点了下一页之后我们知道这事好办了：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/人民网_headingNews2.5a6plmtk5t00.webp" alt="人民网_headingNews2"></p><p>因为我们还是只需要改变链接的一个数字就能实现页面的跳转，我们使用以下代码来试探一下先：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">url3 = <span class="string">&quot;http://world.people.com.cn/&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">r = requests.get(url3, headers=headers, proxies=proxies)</span><br><span class="line">soup = BeautifulSoup(r.content, <span class="string">&quot;html.parser&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">links = soup.select(<span class="string">&#x27;[class=&quot;headingNews&quot;] [class=&quot;hdNews clearfix&quot;] p a&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">links = [link.get(<span class="string">&#x27;href&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">for</span> link <span class="keyword">in</span> links]</span><br><span class="line">links</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>结果如下，我们可以发现有小部分链接是完整的，我们要将这部分链接与其他链接隔离开补充链接前缀。</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/人民网_crawl_result1.7lau2jm392s0.webp" alt="人民网_crawl_result1"></p><p>我们补充完细节后该部分完整代码为：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">link_renminwang = []</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">3</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    url = <span class="string">&quot;http://world.people.com.cn/index&quot;</span> + <span class="built_in">str</span>(i+<span class="number">1</span>) + <span class="string">&quot;.html&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    r = requests.get(url, headers=headers, proxies=proxies)</span><br><span class="line">    soup = BeautifulSoup(r.content, <span class="string">&quot;html.parser&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    links = soup.select(<span class="string">&#x27;[class=&quot;headingNews&quot;] [class=&quot;hdNews clearfix&quot;] p a&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    links = [link.get(<span class="string">&#x27;href&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">for</span> link <span class="keyword">in</span> links]</span><br><span class="line">    links = [<span class="string">&quot;http://world.people.com.cn&quot;</span> + link <span class="keyword">for</span> link <span class="keyword">in</span> links <span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="string">&quot;people.com.cn&quot;</span> <span class="keyword">not</span> <span class="keyword">in</span> link]</span><br><span class="line">    links = <span class="built_in">list</span>(<span class="built_in">set</span>(links))</span><br><span class="line">    link_renminwang.extend(links)</span><br><span class="line">link_renminwang = <span class="built_in">list</span>(<span class="built_in">set</span>(link_renminwang))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>仅仅是选取了前三个列我们已经获取了193篇重复的文章，下一步我们还是需要对每一篇文章进一步爬取。随意点开一篇文章查看其内容，结果如下：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/人民网_content.k38g6wuzld8.webp" alt="人民网_content"></p><p>现在我们应当能很快地将前面的代码略作修改以获取对应的内容，但当我们做完之后还是遇到了点问题：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/人民网_simple_crawl_problem2.2zt2nmyw4yg0.webp" alt="人民网_simple_crawl_problem2"></p><p>我们发现尽管大多数内容是正常的，仍然有一些内容是乱码的，且有部分内容是空的，也就是之前描述的只有图片和一句话的页面，这些我们可以不用管直接删了就好：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/人民网_null_page.6wuylec2m0w0.webp" alt="人民网_null_page"></p><h2 id="第二个问题解决网站乱码">第二个问题：解决网站乱码</h2><p>那接下来的问题就是乱码究竟是什么情况呢？实际上我们在打开链接的时候发现内容是完全正常的。那么我们很自然就会思考，会不会是编码的问题？实际上Requests 会基于 HTTP 头部对响应的编码作出有根据的推测。当你访问<font color="Purple">r.text</font> 之时，Requests会使用其推测的文本编码。你可以找出 Requests 使用了什么编码，并且能够使用<font color="Purple">r.encoding</font>属性来改变它。我们可以通过这两行代码来判断用<font color="Purple">requests.get</font> 得到的内容的编码：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(r.encoding)  <span class="comment">#查看网页返回的字符集类型</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(r.apparent_encoding) <span class="comment">#自动判断字符集类型</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>结果为：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/人民网_encoding2.28jl1n5j19hc.webp" alt="人民网_encoding2"></p><p>可以发现 Requests推测的文本编码（也就是网页返回即爬取下来后的编码转换）与源网页编码不一致，由此可知其正是导致乱码原因。当源网页编码和爬取下来后的编码转换不一致时，如源网页为gbk编码的字节流，而我们抓取下后程序直接使用utf-8进行编码并输出到存储文件中，这必然会引起乱码，即当源网页编码和抓取下来后程序直接使用处理编码一致时，则不会出现乱码，此时再进行统一的字符编码也就不会出现乱码了。最终爬取的所有网页无论何种编码格式，都转化为utf-8格式进行存储。</p><p>除此之外我们还需要把.content改为.text，因为<strong>content中间存的是字节码，而text中存的是Beautifulsoup根据猜测的编码方式将content内容编码成字符串</strong>。我们修改的编码对content是不起作用的。因此最后该部分代码为：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">text_renminwang = []</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> url_ui <span class="keyword">in</span> tqdm(<span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="built_in">len</span>(link_renminwang))):</span><br><span class="line">    time.sleep(<span class="number">0.5</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    url = link_renminwang[url_ui]</span><br><span class="line">    r = requests.get(url, headers=headers, proxies=proxies)</span><br><span class="line">    r.encoding = <span class="string">&quot;gbk&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    soup = BeautifulSoup(r.text, <span class="string">&quot;html.parser&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    content = soup.select(<span class="string">&#x27;[class=&quot;rm_txt_con cf&quot;] p&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    i_te = <span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> content:</span><br><span class="line">        i_te += i.text</span><br><span class="line">    i_te = i_te.replace(<span class="string">&quot;ADVERTISEMENTADVERTISEMENT&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="built_in">len</span>(i_te) != <span class="number">0</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        text_renminwang.append(i_te)</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">df = pd.DataFrame(text_renminwang)</span><br><span class="line">df.to_excel(<span class="string">&quot;data/renminwang.xlsx&quot;</span>, index=<span class="literal">False</span>, header=<span class="literal">False</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>注意：</strong>区分源网编码 A-gbk、程序直接使用的编码B-ISO-8859-1、统一转换字符的编码 C-utf-8。</p><blockquote><p><strong>知识背景</strong>：在此，我们拓展讲讲unicode、ISO-8859-1、gbk2312、gbk、utf-8等之间的区别联系，大概如下：</p><p>最早的编码是 iso8859-1，和 ascii编码相似。但为了方便表示各种各样的语言，逐渐出现了很多标准编码。iso8859-1属于单字节编码，最多能表示的字符范围是0-255，应用于英文系列。很明显，iso8859-1编码表示的字符范围很窄，无法表示中文字符。</p><p>1981年中国人民通过对 ASCII 编码的中文扩充改造，产生了 GB2312编码，可以表示6000多个常用汉字。但汉字实在是太多了，包括繁体和各种字符，于是产生了GBK 编码，它包括了 GB2312中的编码，同时扩充了很多。中国又是个多民族国家，各个民族几乎都有自己独立的语言系统，为了表示那些字符，继续把GBK 编码扩充为 GB18030编码。每个国家都像中国一样，把自己的语言编码，于是出现了各种各样的编码，如果你不安装相应的编码，就无法解释相应编码想表达的内容。终于，有个叫ISO 的组织看不下去了。他们一起创造了一种编码 UNICODE，这种编码非常大，大到可以容纳世界上任何一个文字和标志。所以只要电脑上有UNICODE 这种编码系统，无论是全球哪种文字，只需要保存文件的时候，保存成UNICODE 编码就可以被其他电脑正常解释。UNICODE在网络传输中，出现了两个标准 UTF-8 和 UTF-16，分别每次传输 8个位和16个位。于是就会有人产生疑问，UTF-8既然能保存那么多文字、符号，为什么国内还有这么多使用 GBK等编码的人？因为 UTF-8等编码体积比较大，占电脑空间比较多，如果面向的使用人群绝大部分都是中国人，用GBK 等编码也可以。</p><p>也可以这样来理解：字符串是由字符构成，字符在计算机硬件中通过二进制形式存储，这种二进制形式就是编码。如果直接使用“字符串↔︎️字符↔︎️二进制表示（编码）”，会增加不同类型编码之间转换的复杂性。所以引入了一个抽象层，“字符串↔︎️字符↔︎️与存储无关的表示↔︎️二进制表示（编码）”，这样，可以用一种与存储无关的形式表示字符，不同的编码之间转换时可以先转换到这个抽象层，然后再转换为其他编码形式。在这里，unicode就是 “与存储无关的表示”，utf—8 就是 “二进制表示”。</p></blockquote><h1 id="新华社网站爬虫实战">新华社网站爬虫实战</h1><p>我们乍一点开新华社的首页，觉得页面内容可能也就和之前那么回事。直接索引<font color="Purple">item-headnews </font>就完事了：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/新华社_first_page.5do5jy1ebec0.webp" alt="新华社_first_page"></p><p>但当我们再进一步点开这些链接的时候，发现真的结果参差不齐，有的是微信公众号里的页面，有的是网页形式的页面，更有的直接是啥也没有，直接报一个404：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/xinhua_微信公众号.2c9oxkry8pj4.webp" alt="xinhua_微信公众号"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/xinhua_normal.2jb8jngwxzc0.webp" alt="xinhua_normal"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/xinhua_404.5oo6cqyouws0.webp" alt="xinhua_404"></p><p>因此为了减轻之后数据清洗的压力，我们需要进一步探索页面找到合适的可以爬取的对象，我们挖呀挖呀挖终于找到一个叫<a class="link" href="http://www.news.cn/comments/index.html">新华网评<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a>的页面，该页面形式如下：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/xinhua_网评.w6chwo9sek0.webp" alt="xinhua_网评"></p><p>我们从这个页面可以看到几个关键点，第一是有些部分前面打了标签——组图，这些内容也正是和前面爬取人民网的时候一样，是只有极少量的文字的，是我们不需要的对象。第二是页面下方有一个加载更多按键，我们猜测是和之前处理的情况是一样的，我们需要进行抓包操作：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/xinhua_加载更多.11wq73qupo0w.webp" alt="xinhua_加载更多"></p><h1 id="参考链接">参考链接</h1><ol type="1"><li><a class="link" href="http://c.biancheng.net/python_spider/case06.html">Python爬虫抓取动态加载数据<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a></li><li><a class="link" href="https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/article/1429372">Python乱码问题怎么解决<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a></li><li><a class="link" href="https://www.eolink.com/news/post/15835.html">pythonrequests返回对象的content和text方法的区别<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
