    <published>2023-06-01T04:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-06-10T15:06:59.234Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="hexo部署命令及坑点">Hexo部署命令及坑点</h1><h1 id="域名购买流程及坑点">域名购买流程及坑点</h1><h1 id="git命令及坑点">Git命令及坑点</h1><p>我们前面提过，当我们想要更新博客时需要使用一键三连命令：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>但有时候网络不好，可能会导致我们的博客屡次无法成功（如下图所示），报错为<font color="Green">Failedto connect to github.com port 443:connection timed out</font>&gt;</p><figure><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/commit时遇到connect问题.tsvozp8fo2o.webp" alt="commit时遇到connect问题"><figcaption aria-hidden="true">commit时遇到connect问题</figcaption></figure><p>如果你的电脑配置了梯子，那么可以选择以下命令设置代理来解决问题：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global http.proxy http://127.0.0.1:7890</span><br><span class="line">git config --global https.proxy http://127.0.0.1:7890</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>另外当你想要取消全局代理的时候也可以通过类似命令完成：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global --unset http.proxy</span><br><span class="line">git config --global --unset https.proxy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>除此之外也有一些其他的解决方案，我将参考链接列在下面：</p><ol type="1"><li><p><a class="link" href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_42902669/article/details/114699679?spm=1001.2101.3001.6650.5&amp;utm_medium=distribute.pc_relevant.none-task-blog-2%7Edefault%7ECTRLIST%7ERate-5-114699679-blog-103226958.235%5Ev38%5Epc_relevant_anti_t3&amp;depth_1-utm_source=distribute.pc_relevant.none-task-blog-2%7Edefault%7ECTRLIST%7ERate-5-114699679-blog-103226958.235%5Ev38%5Epc_relevant_anti_t3&amp;utm_relevant_index=4">風の唄を聴け提出的三种解决方案<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a></p></li><li><p><a class="link" href="https://blog.csdn.net/Hodors/article/details/103226958">该部分内容参考的fK0pS提出的设置代理方法<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a></p></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
